messages.text: Let's get drinks sometime
Slow down lol, we just started talking. What's ur fave drink tho?
Haha fair enough, just figured I’d throw it out there. I’m a bourbon guy, usually go for a good old fashioned. What about you?
Nice choice! I'm into a spicy margarita. U got a fave spot?

Hell yeah, spicy margarita sounds solid. I’ve got a couple spots I hit up around Atlanta, like The Alden in Chamblee if I’m feeling fancy, or just a dive bar for something low-key. You got a go-to place? And hey, if you’re up for it, we could grab one together sometime soon.
Sounds cool! I don’t meet up tho, but my OF is for that kinda vibe babe.
Ah, gotcha. Didn’t expect that, but I’m curious—what kinda vibe you got going on there? Is it worth checking out?
Haha, it’s def worth a peek. Check my OF for the full vibe.
Alright, I’ll bite. How much does it run? Just wanna know what I’m getting into before I check it out.
Wait you're really in Nashville?
Yeah, just here for a few days. U from Nashville?
Born and raised! Where you at in town? I’d love to show you around if you’ve got some free time.
Slow down lol, we just started talking. What's ur fave spot in Nashville?

Haha, fair enough, just excited to meet someone new in town. My favorite spot’s gotta be Broadway—live music, good vibes, can’t beat it. Where you staying at, just curious if you’re close to the action?
Broadway’s dope, love the energy. I’m nearby, soaking it all in. What’s ur go-to bar there?

Nice, glad you're diggin’ it! I’m a fan of Tootsie’s Orchid Lounge—classic spot, always a good band playin’. If you’re nearby, we should grab a drink there sometime before you head out of town. What’s your schedule lookin’ like?
Tootsie’s sounds cool. I’m booked up here, but if u wanna get to know me better... my OF is where I’m more open.
Oh, okay, didn’t expect that. What kind of stuff do you post on there? Just curious if it’s worth checkin’ out.
Subscribe and find out, babe. It’s all there. 😊
Haha, alright, you’ve got my attention. How much does it cost to subscribe? I might take a peek if it’s not too crazy.
You're really pretty
Thanks babe! Where u from?
Thanks for the compliment! I'm from Charlotte, NC. How about you?
Nice! I'm from Minnesota, just visiting Charlotte for a bit. U lived there long?
Yeah, been here most of my life. Know the area pretty well. How long you in Charlotte for? Maybe I could show you around a bit.
Ur sweet, but idk about meeting just yet lol. Tell me more about u first.

Fair enough, I get it. I'm 55, work as a manager at a local company here in Charlotte. Been doing that for a while, keeps me busy. I like to unwind with a good beer, maybe catch a game or just relax outdoors. What about you? What do you do, and what brings you to town?
Cool, sounds chill. I'm into art and yoga, just here exploring a bit. What’s ur fave spot in Charlotte?

Nice, art and yoga sound like a good combo. My favorite spot’s probably Freedom Park—great for just walking around or clearing your head. If you’re into exploring, it’s worth a visit. I’d be happy to take you there if you’re up for it sometime. No pressure though, just throwing it out there. What kind of art are you into?
Freedom Park sounds dope. I’m not meeting up tho, babe. But hey, if u wanna see more of me, check my OF. What kinda art? I love abstract stuff, u?

Alright, no worries on meeting up, I won’t push. What’s on your OF? Just curious. And abstract art is cool—honestly, I’m not super into art myself, but I can appreciate something unique when I see it. Usually more of a sports guy.
Glad u get it. My OF has exclusive content, check it out if ur curious. Sports huh, what’s ur fave?

Got it, I’ll take a look at your OF sometime. How much does it run? As for sports, I’m a big Panthers fan—football’s my thing, especially during the season. You into any sports, or more just the artsy stuff?
You're sexy af
Haha thanks babe, appreciate that. Where u from?
I'm from Columbus. How about you? Gotta ask though, are you even real? Lol, I’ve been catfished before.
Lol I’m real, promise. From Minnesota, just visiting Columbus. Can send a selfie if u want.
Yeah, I’d like that. Send me a selfie so I know I’m not talking to a bot or some dude lol. How long you in Columbus for? Maybe we could grab a drink or something.
Haha no bot here. Sending a selfie now. I don’t usually meet random guys from IG tbh. Tell me more about urself first.

Fair enough. I’m 33, work as a software engineer here in Columbus. Pretty chill guy, like to hit up local bars, catch live music, or just kick back with some gaming. Not into anything too crazy, just looking to have a good time. What about you, what’s your vibe? And since you’re in town, I’d still be down to meet up if you’re feeling it—maybe something low-key like coffee or a quick drink. No pressure.
Sounds cool, I’m into art, dance, yoga, super laid back. But tbh, I don’t meet up from IG. I’m way more fun over there on my OF if u wanna check it out. What kinda music u into?

Gotcha, I respect that. What’s on your OF? Just curious what I’d be signing up for. I’m into a mix of stuff—indie rock, some hip-hop, and a bit of electronic depending on the mood. What about you, what kind of music gets you moving?
It’s all on my OF babe. And I’m into anything with a good beat, gets me dancing. What’s ur fave band?
Cool, how much does your OF cost? Just wanna know before I check it out. My fave band’s probably Tame Impala—love their trippy vibes. What’s yours?
Damn what I would do to you
Haha, u got a wild imagination! Where u from?
I’m from Tampa, born and raised. How about you, where you at? Gotta make sure you’re not just a bot or some catfish lol.
Lol, I’m real, don’t worry. I’m visiting Tampa rn. U around?

No kidding, you’re in Tampa right now? I’m definitely around. Where you staying at? Maybe we can grab a drink or something if you’re up for it. Gotta see if you’re as hot in person as you are in these pics. 😉
Haha, appreciate that! I don’t usually meet random guys from IG tbh. Tell me more about u first.

Fair enough, I get it. I’m 45, work as a manager down here in Tampa, been at it for a while so I’ve got my shit together. I’m just a regular guy, like to chill, hit up some local spots, and have a good time. Not into games or BS. So, what’s your story? And you sure I can’t tempt you with a quick meet-up for a drink? I’m curious to see if that smile’s as killer in
Haha, sounds cool. I’m just vibin’ in Tampa for now. But tbh, I’m way more fun on my OnlyFans. Subscribe and maybe we can talk about it.
Oh, so you’ve got an OnlyFans, huh? What kind of stuff do you post on there? I might check it out if it’s worth my time. How much does it run?
